text.tspan: The set of matrix product state families is equal to
the set of rational state families!
The set of infinite matrix product states is equal to
the set of rational infinite states!
There are two significant implications of these results. First, we
have fully characterized the set of matrix product state families
and the set of infinite matrix product states in terms of the closure
of rational operators on state families. Second, conversely, we have
obtained a means of defining expectation functions on a well-
characterized subset of infinite states by using matrix product states.
